import React from 'react'

export default function Moon() {
    return (
        <svg
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        width="24"
        height="24"
        fill="none"
        stroke="currentColor"
        strokeWidth="2"
        strokeLinecap="round"
        strokeLinejoin="round"
      >
        <path d="M21 12.79A9 9 0 1 1 11.21 3 7 7 0 0 0 21 12.79z"></path>
      </svg>
    )
}
